{"type": "article", "id": 1271, "title": "把“世界杯”挂在家里", "description": "", "date": "2014-06-26T09:10:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 139, "name": "涂鸦"}, {"id": 710, "name": "世界杯"}], "category": 12, "author": 13, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604215501fxMaQJy2dZC9hOnT.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t有没有觉得再精彩的世界杯进球瞬间，也不值得挂在家里作为装饰？即便给它装上框，看上去也实在很像大学宿舍的标配。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t艺术家们现在来帮助你把这件事做得高级一点，从摄影作品到抽象表现主义，既能和室内设计相融，也满足你所好。这些艺术家包括以涂鸦见长的Keith Haring和巴斯奎特。涂鸦和在巴西一向作为街头运动的足球还的确是蛮搭的。你可以在<a href=\"http://www.esquire.co.uk/culture/article/6539/world-cup-art/\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>看看有没有值得悬挂的钟意作品。实在钟意的话，也可以<a href=\"http://www.art.co.uk/gallery/id--b7279/fifa-world-cup-prints.htm?ui=6DBEA8E19369482098369FFBAB4B5B28\" target=\"_blank\">下个单</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215458dEgAYeon95mcBHtK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215459TFR3geMciDEkd0rB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215500XI2geqQnOlVc4Tbi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}